Varga Says ‘Hard to Assess’ Flat Tax Effectiveness in Hungary

-- B y   Z o l t a n   S i m o n
-- 
2011-09-29T12:56:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/varga-says-hard-to-assess-flat-tax-effectiveness-in-hungary.html
The effectiveness of the flat
personal income tax, which was introduced in  Hungary  this year,
is “hard to assess,”  Mihaly Varga , Prime Minister  Viktor
Orban ’s chief of staff, said at a conference in Pecs, southern
Hungary today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
